{"tid":2070481,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇MBC同BIG HIT冷戰?","createTime":"2020-06-19T07:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T08:57:31.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16043d3238c70397a30503a9bb94516ea986439f","tid":2070481,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"BIG HIT旗下既團冇得上音中<br />\n<br />\nSeventeen即將發行新專輯回歸之際,將無法MBC音樂節目《SHOW！ 音樂中心》中見到他們。<br />\n這被解釋為是Big Hit和MBC之間矛盾的餘波。雙方因在2018年末《MBC歌謠大祭典》的出演問題上而產生矛盾,從去年5月就見不到BIG HIT所屬歌手出演《SHOW! 音樂中心》。<br />\n在這種情況下,今年5月Pledis加入BIG HIT旗下,Seventeen發行新專輯果然也無法在《Show! 音樂中心》中見到。由此可見Big Hit和MBC的矛盾還在繼續。<br />\n<br />\nMBC就話自己邀請左但BIG HIT唔受<br />\n<br />\nMBC音樂中心官方表示&quot;雖然邀請了SEVENTEEN出演但未能實現，希望他們出演&quot;<br />\n下面是MBC官方立場<br />\n大家好。這裡是MBC《Show! 音樂中心》。<br />\n《Show!音樂中心》製作組正致力於邀請多樣類型的歌手,展現與現有音樂節目不同的舞台。<br />\n此前製作組曾邀請Seventeen出演,希望他們能為觀眾們表演舞台。<br />\n今後,《SHOW! 音樂中心》製作團隊將為K-POP粉絲展現出最棒的舞台而努力。<br />\n<br />\n我自己就唔係幾信MBC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f4d84d6d89f150bd0570209942374f38849659","tid":2070481,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:15:54.000Z","msg":"你 = big hit狗"},{"pid":"39cc9e892b81c00108c4a47cdad0c26d1276b07f","tid":2070481,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4f4d84d6d89f150bd0570209942374f38849659","tid":2070481,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:15:54.000Z","msg":"你 = big hit狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:18:05.000Z","msg":"唔係啦 我公平公開咁討論下姐"},{"pid":"0911d644e76514067bd9cebb99d8f6bcaa737a4d","tid":2070481,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"MBC咁小氣嫁&hellip;"},{"pid":"0d3ace8fe02eed08faa8a45302b71e888e80c3e8","tid":2070481,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4f4d84d6d89f150bd0570209942374f38849659","tid":2070481,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,